<section data-depth="1" id="fs-idp75946800" class="exercises"><h3 data-type="title">Chemistry End of Chapter Exercises</h3><div data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp18527664">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idm31250240">
<p id="fs-idp75695024">Which bond in each of the following pairs of bonds is the strongest?</p>
<p id="fs-idp174181168">(a) C&#8211;C or <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mtext>C</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>C</mtext></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mtext>C</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>C</mtext></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idp191457408">(b) C&#8211;N or <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mtext>C</mtext><mo>&#8801;</mo><mtext>N</mtext></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mtext>C</mtext><mo>&#8801;</mo><mtext>N</mtext></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idm37995600">(c)<math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mtext>C</mtext><mo>&#8801;</mo><mtext>O</mtext></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mtext>C</mtext><mo>&#8801;</mo><mtext>O</mtext></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> or <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mtext>C</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>O</mtext></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mtext>C</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>O</mtext></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idp19512320">(d) H&#8211;F or H&#8211;Cl</p>
<p id="fs-idm2333776">(e) C&#8211;H or O&#8211;H</p>
<p id="fs-idp120232048">(f) C&#8211;N or C&#8211;O</p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-idp16780032">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-idp37241056">
<p id="fs-idm20426752">Using the bond energies in <a href="#fs-idp13638832" class="autogenerated-content">[link]</a>, determine the approximate enthalpy change for each of the following reactions:</p>
<p id="fs-idp13624240">(a) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>Br</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mn>2</mn><mtext>HBr</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mrow><mtext>Br</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mn>2</mn><mtext>HBr</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idm48592992">(b) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>CH</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>I</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><msub><mrow><mtext>CH</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mtext>I</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mtext>HI</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>CH</mtext></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><msub><mtext>I</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><msub><mrow><mtext>CH</mtext></mrow><mn>3</mn></msub><mtext>I</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mtext>HI</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
<p id="fs-idm27033728">(c) <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mtext>C</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>4</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><msub><mtext>O</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mn>2</mn><msub><mrow><mtext>CO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>O</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mtext>C</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>4</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><msub><mtext>O</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mo stretchy="false">&#10230;</mo><mspace width="0.2em"/><mn>2</mn><msub><mrow><mtext>CO</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mtext>H</mtext><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>O</mtext><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-idp55504208">
<p id="fs-idm5136112">(a) &#8722;114 kJ; (b) 30 kJ; (c) &#8722;1055 kJ</p></div>
</div>
